{"tid":217433,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連囝又話有失實指控會del post嘅","createTime":"2017-04-25T18:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T04:19:42.000Z","uid":14719,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80f7bf53279707d2fff0f793211be70d8257df7a","tid":217433,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T18:26:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我們團隊希望會員在對他人作出這種嚴重指控前審慎思考理據，小心求証，以避免有人被無辜牽連。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本討論區著重言論自由，若內容有充足理據支持，我們絕不會無故刪除有關內容。但我們也不希望當中有無辜人仕在無充份証明下遭受如此嚴重的指控</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解呢個post話明林鄭死咗都冇del post架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/182282/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/182282/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"37ec4974f3e77f4238952a1c70b189ccbe640b6a","tid":217433,"uid":8985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T23:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a77d34274dd0a3382fe8b9526c535afff255fa","tid":217433,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T23:41:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82b246a20b85eae2db54334db5bc3e4265c87130","tid":217433,"uid":72567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T23:49:18.000Z","msg":"蛾非娥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d140c24592bc2fb57893b09ec75b635b3eabb60","tid":217433,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:19:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蛾非娥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國香港第4屆行政長官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}